on the bench.

1236
01:13:52,053 --> 01:13:55,180
And I waited an hour,
two hours, three hours.

1237
01:13:55,348 --> 01:13:58,475
Finally, turned around,
went home. I left.

1238
01:14:00,686 --> 01:14:02,854
