what did he say?

1251
01:14:47,150 --> 01:14:49,818
He used "fuck" a lot.

1252
01:14:49,986 --> 01:14:51,027
[PEOPLE LAUGHING]

1253
01:14:51,195 --> 01:14:53,155
And "piss on you."

1254
01:14:53,573 --> 01:14:57,742
And said he was "gonna bunghole
the short-order chef."

1255
01:14:57,910 --> 01:15:00,662
