1259
01:15:07,962 --> 01:15:11,173
Oh? What is that?
I'm a diabetic.

1260
01:15:11,716 --> 01:15:13,341
[PEOPLE LAUGHING]

1261
01:15:13,509 --> 01:15:15,510
I fail to see the connection.

1262
01:15:15,678 --> 01:15:18,263
