causing foul language.

1263
01:15:18,431 --> 01:15:20,932
That's because you're
a douchebag.

1264
01:15:21,100 --> 01:15:22,726
[PEOPLE LAUGHING]

1265
01:15:27,398 --> 01:15:29,524
