I'm just not in a good mood,
you know?

1285
01:16:27,833 --> 01:16:31,169
Frank.
Yeah, here I am. Is that it?

1286
01:16:31,337 --> 01:16:32,420
Yeah, that's it.

1287
01:16:32,588 --> 01:16:34,172
I'll get back to you
on Fenwick.

1288
01:16:34,340 --> 01:16:36,007
All right.
Gotta talk to you.

1289
01:16:36,175 --> 01:16:37,926
