This punk kept pulling
my wife's purse

1292
01:16:45,017 --> 01:16:47,018
and she wouldn't let go.

1293
01:16:47,186 --> 01:16:48,979
So I tried to get him off.

1294
01:16:49,146 --> 01:16:50,647
